{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"那个小弟，真的就叫做小弟？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":15,"line_end":15},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"不管他是不是叫小弟，他都绝不是个小弟。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":21,"line_end":21},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"不是！","tone":"认真","chapter":35,"line_start":23,"line_end":23},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"他已是个男子汉。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":25,"line_end":25},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"你认为他是？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":27,"line_end":27},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"我只知道，如果我是他，很可能就不会把那封信说出来！","tone":"认真","chapter":35,"line_start":29,"line_end":29},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":31,"line_end":31},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"因为我也知道他是天尊的人，他的母亲就是慕容秋荻。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":33,"line_end":33},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"我还知道一件事！","tone":"激动","chapter":35,"line_start":37,"line_end":37},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"什么事？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":39,"line_end":39},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"他来救你，你很高兴，并不是因为他救了你的命，而是因为他来了！","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":41,"line_end":41},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"还有件事你可以放心，我绝不会再去找薛可人。","tone":"认真","chapter":35,"line_start":49,"line_end":49},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"因为她虽然做错了，却是被逼的，而且她已经赎了罪。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":51,"line_end":51},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"可是……","tone":"犹豫","chapter":35,"line_start":53,"line_end":53},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"可是你一定要去找她。","tone":"认真","chapter":35,"line_start":55,"line_end":55},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"虽然我不去找她，你却一定要去找她。","tone":"严肃","chapter":35,"line_start":57,"line_end":57},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"我一定会去找她。","tone":"认真","chapter":35,"line_start":65,"line_end":65},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"另外有个人，你却一定不能去找。","tone":"严肃","chapter":35,"line_start":67,"line_end":67},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":69,"line_end":69},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"燕十三。","tone":"沉声","chapter":35,"line_start":71,"line_end":71}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":101,"line_end":200,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"你这一生中，见到过的最可怕的一个人是谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":101,"line_end":101},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"是个我从未见过的陌生人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":103,"line_end":103},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"陌生人并不可怕。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":105,"line_end":105},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"但是这个陌生人却和别的人不同。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":113,"line_end":113},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"有什么不同？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":115,"line_end":115},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"你是在哪里见到他的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":119,"line_end":119},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"在一个陌生的地方。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":121,"line_end":121},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"你想那个陌生人会不会是燕十三？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":129,"line_end":129},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"很可能。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":131,"line_end":131},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"我这一生中，见到过的最可怕的一个人也是他，不是你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":133,"line_end":133},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"不是我？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":35,"line_start":135,"line_end":135},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"因为你毕竟还是个人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":137,"line_end":137},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"燕十三却不是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":143,"line_end":143},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"他不是人？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":35,"line_start":145,"line_end":145},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"绝不是。","tone":"肯定","chapter":35,"line_start":147,"line_end":147},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"他没有朋友，没有亲人，他虽然对我很好，传授我的剑法，可是却从来不让我亲近他，也从来不让我知道他从哪里来，要往哪里去。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":151,"line_end":151},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"夺命十三剑中的第十四种变化，并不是你创出来的。","tone":"认真","chapter":35,"line_start":161,"line_end":161},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"是他！","tone":"肯定","chapter":35,"line_start":163,"line_end":163},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"他早已知道这十四剑，而且也早已知道你剑中有一处破绽。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":165,"line_end":165},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"可是他没有传授给你？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":167,"line_end":167},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"他没有。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":169,"line_end":169},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"你认为他是在藏私？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":171,"line_end":171},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"我知道他不是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":173,"line_end":173},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"你也知道他是为了什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":175,"line_end":175},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"因为他生怕我学会这一剑后，会去找你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":177,"line_end":177},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"因为他自己对这一剑也没有把握？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":179,"line_end":179},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"可是你也同样没有把握能破他的这一剑。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":181,"line_end":181},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"我知道你没有把握，因为刚才我使出那一剑时，你若有把握，早已出手，也就不会遭人的暗算。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":185,"line_end":185},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"我劝你不要去找他，就因为你们全都没有把握，我不想看着你们自相残杀，两败俱伤。","tone":"认真","chapter":35,"line_start":189,"line_end":189},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"一个人在临死前的那一瞬间，想的是什么事？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":192,"line_end":192},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"是不是会想起他这一生中所有的亲人和往事？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":195,"line_end":195},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"不是。","tone":"否定","chapter":35,"line_start":197,"line_end":197},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"本来我也认为应该是的，可是我自知必死的那瞬间，想到的却不是这些事。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":199,"line_end":199}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":201,"line_end":280,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"你想的是什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":201,"line_end":201},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"是那一剑，第十四剑。","tone":"认真","chapter":35,"line_start":203,"line_end":203},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"本来我的确没把握能破那一剑，可是在那一瞬间，我心里却好像忽然有道闪电击过，那一剑本来的确是无坚不摧无懈可击，可是被这道闪电一击，立刻就变了！","tone":"激动","chapter":35,"line_start":209,"line_end":209},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"变得怎么样？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":211,"line_end":211},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"变得很可笑。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":35,"line_start":213,"line_end":213},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"好酒。","tone":"欣慰","chapter":35,"line_start":221,"line_end":221},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"偷来的酒，通常都是好酒。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":35,"line_start":223,"line_end":223},{"speaker":"char_tie_kai_cheng","speaker_name":"铁开诚","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"今日一别，不知要等到何时才能再醉。","tone":"无奈","chapter":35,"line_start":225,"line_end":225},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_tie_kai_cheng","text":"只要你真的想醉，何时不能再醉！","tone":"豪迈","chapter":35,"line_start":227,"line_end":227},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_xiao_di","text":"可惜你没有跟我们一起去喝酒，那真是好酒。","tone":"微笑","chapter":35,"line_start":251,"line_end":251},{"speaker":"char_xiao_di","speaker_name":"小弟","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"偷来的酒，通常都是好酒。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":253,"line_end":253},{"speaker":"char_xiao_di","speaker_name":"小弟","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"只可惜不管多好的酒，也治不了你的伤。","tone":"认真","chapter":35,"line_start":259,"line_end":259},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_xiao_di","text":"幸好有些伤是根本就不必去治的。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":35,"line_start":263,"line_end":263},{"speaker":"char_xiao_di","speaker_name":"小弟","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"什么伤？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":265,"line_end":265},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_xiao_di","text":"根本就治不好的伤。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":267,"line_end":267},{"speaker":"char_xiao_di","speaker_name":"小弟","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"你醉了。","tone":"平静","chapter":35,"line_start":269,"line_end":269},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_xiao_di","text":"你也醉了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":271,"line_end":271},{"speaker":"char_xiao_di","speaker_name":"小弟","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"哦？","tone":"疑问","chapter":35,"line_start":273,"line_end":273},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_xiao_di","text":"你应该知道，天下最容易摆脱的是哪种人？","tone":"认真","chapter":35,"line_start":275,"line_end":275},{"speaker":"char_xiao_di","speaker_name":"小弟","listener":"char_xie_xiao_feng","text":"当然是死人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":35,"line_start":277,"line_end":277},{"speaker":"char_xie_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"谢晓峰","listener":"char_xiao_di","text":"你若没有醉，那么你一心要摆脱我，为什么偏偏又要来救我？","tone":"认真","chapter":35,"line_start":279,"line_end":279}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":4,"line_start":281,"line_end":389,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xiao_di","speaker_name":"小弟","listener":null,"text":"怎么样？","tone":"冷酷","chapter":35,"line_start":325,"line_end":325},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"十几个人","listener":"char_xiao_di","text":"不行。","tone":"恐惧","chapter":35,"line_start":327,"line_end":327},{"speaker":"char_xiao_di","speaker_name":"小弟","listener":null,"text":"没有法子？","tone":"冷酷","chapter":35,"line_start":331,"line_end":331},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"十几个人","listener":"char_xiao_di","text":"没有。","tone":"恐惧","chapter":35,"line_start":333,"line_end":333},{"speaker":"char_xiao_di","speaker_name":"小弟","listener":"char_jian_fu_sheng","text":"你就是简复生？","tone":"冷酷","chapter":35,"line_start":341,"line_end":341},{"speaker":"char_jian_fu_sheng","speaker_name":"简复生","listener":"char_xiao_di","text":"是。","tone":"恐惧","chapter":35,"line_start":343,"line_end":343},{"speaker":"char_xiao_di","speaker_name":"小弟","listener":"char_jian_fu_sheng","text":"听说别人都叫你'起死复生'简大先生？","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":35,"line_start":345,"line_end":345},{"speaker":"char_jian_fu_sheng","speaker_name":"简复生","listener":"char_xiao_di","text":"那是别人胡乱吹嘘，老朽实在不敢当。","tone":"恐惧","chapter":35,"line_start":347,"line_end":347},{"speaker":"char_xiao_di","speaker_name":"小弟","listener":"char_jian_fu_sheng","text":"你这鼻烟壶很不错呀！","tone":"微笑","chapter":35,"line_start":349,"line_end":349},{"speaker":"char_xiao_di","speaker_name":"小弟","listener":"char_jian_fu_sheng","text":"这好像还是用整块汉玉雕出来的，只怕最少也值得上千两银子。","tone":"微笑","chapter":35,"line_start":359,"line_end":359},{"speaker":"char_jian_fu_sheng","speaker_name":"简复生","listener":"char_xiao_di","text":"想不到大少爷也是识货的人。","tone":"得意","chapter":35,"line_start":363,"line_end":363},{"speaker":"char_xiao_di","speaker_name":"小弟","listener":"char_jian_fu_sheng","text":"你哪里来的这么多银子！","tone":"厉声","chapter":35,"line_start":365,"line_end":365},{"speaker":"char_jian_fu_sheng","speaker_name":"简复生","listener":"char_xiao_di","text":"都是病人送的诊金！","tone":"恐惧","chapter":35,"line_start":367,"line_end":367},{"speaker":"char_xiao_di","speaker_name":"小弟","listener":"char_jian_fu_sheng","text":"看来你收的诊金可真不少呀！","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":35,"line_start":369,"line_end":369},{"speaker":"char_xiao_di","speaker_name":"小弟","listener":"char_jian_fu_sheng","text":"你能不能借给我看看？","tone":"微笑","chapter":35,"line_start":373,"line_end":373},{"speaker":"char_xiao_di","speaker_name":"小弟","listener":"char_jian_fu_sheng","text":"好，真是好东西，只可惜像你这样的人，还不配用这样的好东西。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":35,"line_start":379,"line_end":379},{"speaker":"char_xiao_di","speaker_name":"小弟","listener":"char_jian_fu_sheng","text":"你既称名医，收的诊金比谁都高，却连这么样一点轻伤都治不好，你究竟是他妈的什么东西？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":35,"line_start":387,"line_end":387}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_jian_fu_sheng","name":"简复生","alias":["起死复生简大先生"],"identity":"名医","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"healer","rank":null,"one_line":"被称为'起死复生'的名医，贪财势利，在小弟面前畏缩如鼠","personality":{"traits":["贪财","势利","胆小","虚伪","圆滑"],"speech_style":"恭敬谄媚，面对权势时结结巴巴","temperament":"怯懦"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[35],"source_refs":[{"chapter":35,"line_start":337,"line_end":389,"text":"这人年纪最大，气派不小，手里拿着的一个鼻烟壶，至少就已价值千金。……简复生全身发抖，满身冷汗，嘴里结结巴巴的不知在说什么。"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[{"id":"item_bi_yu_bi_yan_hu","name":"碧玉鼻烟壶","type":"special","owner":"char_jian_fu_sheng","one_line":"简复生随身携带的碧玉鼻烟壶，价值千金","description":"整块碧玉雕成的鼻烟壶，雕工精美，价值连城，简复生时时刻刻带在身边，就连睡着了都压在枕头下面，后被小弟摔碎。","effects":[],"origin":"病人赠送的诊金所购","rarity":"稀世珍品","related_characters":["char_jian_fu_sheng"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[35],"source_refs":[{"chapter":35,"line_start":337,"line_end":381,"text":"手里拿着的一个鼻烟壶，至少就已价值千金。……这价值连城的鼻烟壶竟已被摔在地上，摔得粉碎。"}]}]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_xiao_di","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":35,"line_start":313,"line_end":317,"text":"小弟终于出现了。前些日子来，他一直显得很疲倦憔悴，落魄潦倒。可是现在他却已换上一身鲜明华丽的衣服，连发髻都梳得很光洁整齐。"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_xie_xiao_feng","type":"宿敌","intensity":70,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"对谢晓峰态度复杂，既想摆脱又忍不住相救"}]}]}
